This project contains an original smart band demo application implemented in
C and LVGL for openvela/NuttX. The submitted source tree is limited to the
smart band demo workspace and does not include the openvela SDK, NuttX, LVGL,
libuv, Android Emulator, QEMU, toolchains, board support packages, or other
upstream system components.

Project boundary:

- Original application code: openvela_app/smart_band
- Browser-only demonstration: demo
- Reproducibility and demo documents: docs
- Local test helper: tests
- Sensor validation helper: scripts

Project visual assets:

- openvela_app/smart_band/assets/generated_icons/*.png
- openvela_app/smart_band/assets/capybara_lotus_reference.png

